How to use:

Try to run the examples under "C:\Program Files 
(x86)\OpenNI\Samples\Bin\", with the oni file path as the argument.
e.g. "C:\Program Files 
(x86)\OpenNI\Samples\Bin\Release\NiUserTracker.exe" c:\xx\left.oni .

